---

<section class="mx-auto py-20 bg-[#f0f6ff]" id="contacto">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="md:flex md:justify-center gap-40">
      <form
        action="https://formspree.io/f/xdkngyrp"
        method="post"
        class="flex flex-col bg-blue-100 p-5 md:p-10 rounded-lg shadow-lg space-y-6"
      >
        <h2 class="text-center text-blue-700 font-bold text-3xl md:text-5xl">
          ¿No sabes dónde empezar?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-center text-slate-700 mx-auto md:w-2/3">
          Diseñamos y desarrollamos soluciones simples y efectivas que amamos.
          ¡Hablemos y veamos cómo podemos ayudarte a crecer!
        </p>

        <div class="md:flex gap-5">
          <div class="w-full">
            <label for="Nombre" class="text-slate-700 block mb-2">
              Nombre <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
            </label>
            <input
              id="Nombre"
              name="Nombre"
              type="text"
              required
              placeholder="Nombre"
              class="w-full placeholder:text-slate-400 bg-[#f0f6ff] py-2 px-2 text-slate-600
                     rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400
                     focus:outline-none"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="w-full">
            <label
              for="Apellido"
              class="text-slate-700 block mb-2 mt-4 md:mt-0"
            >
              Apellido <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
            </label>
            <input
              id="Apellido"
              name="Apellido"
              type="text"
              required
              placeholder="Apellido"
              class="w-full placeholder:text-slate-400 bg-[#f0f6ff] py-2 px-2 text-slate-600
                     rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400
                     focus:outline-none"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full">
          <label for="Correo" class="text-slate-700 block mb-2">
            Correo Electrónico <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
          </label>
          <input
            id="Correo"
            name="Correo"
            type="email"
            required
            placeholder="Correo Electrónico"
            class="w-full placeholder:text-slate-400 bg-[#f0f6ff] py-2 px-2 text-slate-600
                   rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400
                   focus:outline-none"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="w-full">
          <label for="Telefono" class="text-slate-700 block mb-2">
            Teléfono <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
          </label>
          <input
            id="Telefono"
            name="Telefono"
            type="tel"
            required
            placeholder="Teléfono"
            class="w-full placeholder:text-slate-400 bg-[#f0f6ff] py-2 px-2 text-slate-600
                   rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400
                   focus:outline-none"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="w-full">
          <label for="Mensaje" class="text-slate-700 block mb-2">
            Mensaje <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
          </label>
          <textarea
            id="Mensaje"
            name="Mensaje"
            required
            rows="5"
            placeholder="Escribe tu mensaje aquí"
            class="w-full placeholder:text-slate-400 bg-[#f0f6ff] py-2 px-2 text-slate-600
                   rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400
                   focus:outline-none"
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <button
          type="submit"
          class="bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-10 rounded-full
                 hover:bg-blue-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300
                 ease-in-out focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400"
        >
          Contáctanos
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
